---
title: Gorgeous Greens Farro Bowl with Roasted Zucchini & Asparagus
description: Farro, a variety of hulled wheat, is praised for its chewy texture and nutty flavor. To make this bowl shine, we pair the tasty ancient grain with roasted asparagus and zucchini, aromatic onion and garlic, lemony dressing, nutty Parmesan cheese, and crunchy walnuts. Get ready to be bowled over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6076d520912d7429ec352549-cf844b55.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/gorgeous-greens-farro-bowl-6076d520912d7429ec352549-e7921e43.pdf
